OL,6,FThe 72-year-old was unknowingly
OL,7,Fdrugged and raped by her then husband,
OL,8,FDominique Pelicot, who allegedly also
OL,9,Finvited some 50 other men to rape her
OL,10,Fover a nine year period.
OL,12,FFor almost a decade, Dominique Pelicot
OL,13,Fcrushed sleeping pills and anti-
OL,14,Fanxiety medication into his ex-wife's
OL,15,Ffood and drink, while organising for
OL,16,Fstrangers to come over to their home
OL,17,Fand sexually assault his wife after
OL,18,Fmaking contact in an online chatroom.
