OL,6,FDominique Pelicot has admitted to the
OL,7,Fcharges levelled against him, telling
OL,8,Fthe court "I am a rapist, like the
OL,9,Fother men in this room."
OL,11,FPelicot reportedly filmed many of the
OL,12,Falleged crimes against his wife. Video
OL,13,Fevidence of the alleged rapes was
OL,14,Ffound after Dominique Pelicot was
OL,15,Farrested in 2020 for filming up
OL,16,Fwomen's skirts in a supermarket.
OL,18,FOver the past two months of testimony
OL,19,Fthe court has heard from dozens of
OL,20,Faccused men - most of which deny
OL,21,Fraping Ms Pelicot.
