OL,6,FMany of the defendants told the court
OL,7,Fthat they couldn't have imagined that
OL,8,FDominique Pelicot was drugging his
OL,9,Fwife, and that they were told she was
OL,10,Fa willing participant acting out a
OL,11,Fkinky fantasy.
OL,13,FDominique Pelicot denied this, telling
OL,14,Fthe court his co-defendants knew
OL,15,Fexactly what the situation was.
OL,17,FA total of 50 men were identified by
OL,18,Fpolice from films labelled and stored
OL,19,Fby Dominique Pelicot. The men on trial
OL,20,Fface up to 20 years in prison.
